So if you're struggling in one or more of these areas, it might be worth getting rid of all the extra stuff on your main set of keys and sticking with the three keys you really need (house, car, other).

answersResultList.title: Red envelope
answersResultList.resultContent: Carry a red envelope with you in your bag, pocket, or wallet and you can manifest more luck in any area of life that is struggling. Place a symbol of what you want luck in inside the envelope, so paper money, photos, lists, etc. You can also place an envelope in a southeast corner of your home.

answersResultList.title: Crystal
answersResultList.resultContent: Crystals come in all forms - pendants, display pieces, wind chimes, decorative ornaments, and small pocket-sized pieces to carry with you or even place in your bath. Crystals have long been believed to hold healing powers, but they also help with mental clarity. So if you're studying for an exam or preparing for an important event, have a crystal near you at all times.

answersResultList.title: Dragon

This powerful, red-hot creature will give you the strength and courage you need to more successfully pursue your desires.

So if you're struggling in one or more of these areas, it might be worth getting rid of all the extra stuff on your main set of keys and sticking with the three keys you really need (house, car, other).

answersResultList.title: Red envelope
answersResultList.resultContent: Carry a red envelope with you in your bag, pocket, or wallet and you can manifest more luck in any area of life that is struggling. Place a symbol of what you want luck in inside the envelope, so paper money, photos, lists, etc. You can also place an envelope in a southeast corner of your home.

answersResultList.title: Four-leaf clover
answersResultList.resultContent: This classic good luck symbol is a no-brainer to improve your fortune in anything. Of course, the luckiest way to use this is to actually find a four-leaf clover and pick it and preserve in a clear plastic sleeve, but you can also buy items with a real clover or the shape of one.
